---
title: Carb Smart Turkey-Stuffed Peppers with Couscous and Side Salad
description: A mix of spiced turkey and couscous makes a wonderful filling for Middle Eastern-inspired stuffed peppers. This carb smart dinner is full of wholesome veggies.

